么？" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/17/5fdad4151098a1563.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="49748"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">特别选用玩趣搞怪路线，将大家带回千禧年代，传递美好祝福——假日惊喜，无处不在。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ag8leew7/pic_8/' target='_blank'><img alt="新包当道 | Coach早已告别“老气”，Swinger腋下包能火过PARKER么？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdad41513da4504.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="42937"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ag8leew7/pic_9/' target='_blank'><img alt="新包当道 | Coach早已告别“老气”，Swinger腋下包能火过PARKER么？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdad415492da522.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="78174"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><dir class="hw-tnum"><span class="hw-num">2</span></dir><dir class="hw-title">时下正当红：腋下包</dir><p itemprop="description">跟着小编来认识一下这款包，以品牌1900年代经典手袋款型为灵感，采用棒球手套鞣制皮革工艺制作，带来温柔触感，经典复古魅力。<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ag8leew7/pic_10/' target='_blank'><img alt="新包当道 | Coach早已告别“老气”，Swinger腋下包能火过PARKER么？" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/17/5fdad14ed3bdf2160.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="233554"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">顶部拉链短肩带方便单肩背负，也正是当下流行腋下背包方式。同样也可通过可拆卸肩带斜挎，一包两用，基本能满足日常所需。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ag8leew7/pic_11/' target='_blank'><img alt="新包当道 | Coach早已告别“老气”，Swinger腋下包能火过PARKER么？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdad37e7bffe2681.png_e680.jpg" _size="465770"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">包袋一侧配有LOGO徽标铭牌，另一侧配有标志性旋锁扣，封闭状态时拉链头和旋扣锁合为一体，辨识度和安全性指数兼具。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ag8leew7/pic_12/' target='_blank'><img alt="新包当道 | Coach早已告别“老气”，Swinger腋下包能火过PARKER么？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdaf53946698514.png_e680.jpg" _size="455099"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><dir class="hw-tnum"><span class="hw-num">3</span></dir><dir class="hw-title">尺寸&amp;颜色&amp;购买方式</dir><p itemprop="description"><strong>具体尺寸：</strong>可拆卸短包带，垂直长度20.5cm；可拆卸长肩带，垂直长度54.5cm，可用于肩背或斜挎；大小：23.5cm (长) x 14cm (高) x 7cm (宽)。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ag8leew7/pic_13/' target='_blank'><img alt="新包当道 | Coach早已告别“老气”，Swinger腋下包能火过PARKER么？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdaf1ae8ae469734.png_e680.jpg" _size="328350"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">上身效果如下图，杨紫同款：</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ag8leew7/pic_14/' target='_blank'><img alt="新包当道 | Coach早已告别“老气”，Swinger腋下包能火过PARKER么？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdad2d09a9a81353.png_e680.jpg" _size="379508"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><strong>颜色选择：</strong>经典黑白棕三色，极简纯色，肆意百搭，将复古风情与现代美学完美诠释。还有经典老花款，复古韵味更足，棕、蓝、酒红三色可选。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ag8leew7/pic_15/' target='_blank'><img alt="新包当道 | Coach早已告别“老气”，Swinger腋下包能火过PARKER么？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdad33280dfa7936.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="303533"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ag8leew7/pic_16/' target='_blank'><img alt="新包当道 | Coach早已告别“老气”，Swinger腋下包能火过PARKER么？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdad33272ef71432.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="undefined"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">另外还有一款正面饰有苹果图案的Swinger腋下包，昆凌下图同款，目前官网已售罄。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ag8leew7/pic_17/' target='_blank'><img alt="新包当道 | Coach早已告别“老气”，Swinger腋下包能火过PARKER么？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/17/5fdad6b378a85141.jpg_e680.jpg" _size="181436"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><strong>购买方式：</strong>Coach官网、天猫COACH蔻驰官方旗舰店，皮质和老花款新品售价2900元，织物配牛皮款2600元。 <br/></p><dir class="insert-outer " res-data-id="2809850"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="新包当道 | Coach早已告别“老气”，Swinger腋下包能火过PARKER么？" class="res_smzdm" src="//qna.smzdm.com/