y.smzdm.com/202006/08/5eddb6cb8d11a6296.jpg_e680.jpg" /></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">海天酱油老字号特级头道生抽1.28L<strong class="price res_smzdm">49.9元</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm">海天是来自广东佛山的老字号调味品牌，至今已逾300年历史。这款海天特级头道生抽酱油选用东北地区优质非转基因大豆，只取头道酱油，味道鲜美更健康~</span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">京东</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买</span></span></span></span></dir><dir class="insert-outer" res-data-id="2808088"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="酱油的那些事儿" class="res_smzdm" src="https://y.zdmimg.com/201811/13/5beac1d8aef9f7655.jpg_e680.jpg" /></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">李锦记酱油特级头抽头道酿造鲜味凉拌500ml<strong class="price res_smzdm">16.9元</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm">第一道的原汁原味</span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">京东</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买</span></span></span></span></dir><h3>注意，这几款酱油不含防腐剂，所以打开后要冷藏使用，防止发霉。</h3><p itemprop="description">如果想要酱油中的<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/1183/" data-brandid="1183" target="_blank">爱马仕</a>那么你就选他们吧</p><dir class="insert-outer" res-data-id="2808090"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><img alt="酱油的那些事儿" class="res_smzdm" src="https://qna.smzdm.com/202012/16/5fd98aef0d4d66479.jpg_e680.jpg" /></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><span class="card-name res_smzdm">千禾酱油天元有机酱油特级生抽有机认证516mL<strong class="price res_smzdm">298元</strong></span><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">京东</span><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买</span></span></span></span></dir><dir class="insert-outer" res-data-id="2808091"><span class="embed-card main-site res_smzdm"><span class="embed-card-lo